rows.label: qst201819_msg0001
rows.name:
Hello, little Phonex!
I've got some questions for y-

rows.label: qst201819_msg0002
rows.name:
Choke on a bone, human!
I ain't talkin' to the likes of you!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0003
rows.name:
Hey, come on, don't be like that...
It's an emergency, you know!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0004
rows.name:
Look, it won't take a minute.
Won't you please talk to me?

rows.label: qst201819_msg0005
rows.name:
No, I won't. Don't trust humans.
Keep walkin', sunshine!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0006
rows.name:
Man, what a grouch...
He wouldn't even listen!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0007
rows.name:
How about we go back to Mimi,
see if she knows of a solution?

rows.label: qst201819_msg0008
rows.name:
She might give us a clue
about the right approach here.

rows.label: qst201819_msg0009
rows.name:
That's a good idea.
Let's do it!
